#### 5.2.3 寄养订单管理实现

订单管理是系统的核心业务模块，涉及订单的创建、支付、状态流转等关键业务逻辑。订单创建时，系统根据服务项目的单价和寄养天数计算订单金额，若用户选择了优惠券则计算优惠后的实付金额。

后端订单创建的核心实现代码如下：

```java
@Service
public class OrderServiceImpl extends ServiceImpl<OrderMapper, Order>
        implements OrderService {

    @Autowired
    private ServiceItemService serviceItemService;
    @Autowired
    private CouponService couponService;

    @Override
    @Transactional(rollbackFor = Exception.class)
    public Order createOrder(OrderCreateDTO dto) {
        // 查询服务项目信息
        ServiceItem serviceItem = serviceItemService.getById(dto.getServiceId());
        if (serviceItem == null || serviceItem.getStatus() != 1) {
            throw new BusinessException("服务项目不存在或已下架");
        }

        // 计算寄养天数和费用
        long days = ChronoUnit.DAYS.between(dto.getStartDate(), dto.getEndDate());
        if (days <= 0) {
            throw new BusinessException("寄养结束日期必须晚于开始日期");
        }
        BigDecimal totalAmount = serviceItem.getPrice().multiply(BigDecimal.valueOf(days));

        // 处理保险费用
        BigDecimal insuranceAmount = BigDecimal.ZERO;
        if (dto.getNeedInsurance()) {
            insuranceAmount = new BigDecimal("10.00").multiply(BigDecimal.valueOf(days));
        }

        // 处理优惠券
        BigDecimal discountAmount = BigDecimal.ZERO;
        if (dto.getCouponId() != null) {
            discountAmount = couponService.calculateDiscount(
                dto.getCouponId(), totalAmount);
        }

        // 计算实付金额
        BigDecimal actualAmount = totalAmount.add(insuranceAmount)
                                             .subtract(discountAmount);

        // 创建订单
        Order order = new Order();
        order.setOrderNo(generateOrderNo());
        order.setUserId(dto.getUserId());
        order.setPetId(dto.getPetId());
        order.setServiceId(dto.getServiceId());
        order.setShopId(serviceItem.getShopId());
        order.setStartDate(dto.getStartDate());
        order.setEndDate(dto.getEndDate());
        order.setDays((int) days);
        order.setTotalAmount(totalAmount);
        order.setInsuranceAmount(insuranceAmount);
        order.setCouponId(dto.getCouponId());
        order.setDiscountAmount(discountAmount);
        order.setActualAmount(actualAmount);
        order.setSpecialRequirements(dto.getSpecialRequirements());
        order.setStatus(OrderStatus.PENDING_PAY.getCode());
        order.setPayStatus(0);
        order.setCreateTime(LocalDateTime.now());
        order.setUpdateTime(LocalDateTime.now());
        this.save(order);

        // 标记优惠券已使用
        if (dto.getCouponId() != null) {
            couponService.useCoupon(dto.getCouponId(), dto.getUserId());
        }

        return order;
    }

    private String generateOrderNo() {
        return "PB" + System.currentTimeMillis()
             + String.format("%04d", new Random().nextInt(10000));
    }
}
```

